# ExtremeGEOTools Development Rules

## Code Style

- Use descriptive variable names
- Add docstrings to all functions
- Use comments effectively

## Architecture
- Keep frontend components small and focused
- Implement proper error handling
- Add logging for debugging
- avoid emoji use whenever possible
- Keep changes minimal, unless prompted to do a full overhaul or refactoring

## Testing
- Write unit tests for new features
- Test API endpoints with proper status codes
- Validate data schemas

## Documentation
- Update README.md for new features
- Document API changes in docs/
- Add inline comments for complex logic
- Update codebase_structure.md when creating new folders, files, subfolders